one of this one almost looks like a neutral to me - but with a little bit of extra spice. \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eAnd secondly, you can nab this compact tech accessory for less than £30 – £29 to be exact. What a bargain! Even some of the most budget-friendly speakers won’t be able to compete with that kind of price point.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Stylish home tech, especially speakers, has transformed from mere functional gadgets into essential design elements that fit right into our living spaces,’ says Uriel Tannen, \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.withflitch.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-url=\"https://www.withflitch.com/\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"none\"\u003eFlitch\u003c/a\u003e co-founder and tech expert.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Today, people look for technology that enhances their decor, such as a retro-inspired speaker adding charm to a mid-century modern living room, or a sleek, minimalist design perfectly complementing a Scandi aesthetic. Beautifully designed speakers not only elevate our listening experience but also become eye-catching statement pieces, reflecting personal taste and making a room feel thoughtfully curated rather than cluttered.’\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU.jpg\" alt=\"The IKEA NATTBAD bluetooth speaker in pink on a kitchen shelf against a tonal wall\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/hY5bchp9icEMAXmGSWq3ZU.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: IKEA)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eAnother impressive feature is the multi-speaker function which allows you to connect multiple NATTBAD speakers to your phone or computer to be able to spread the sound even further.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-r54kvNejJKFyo4Wjz86Brb\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eAnd IKEA has been doing an outstanding job at providing its customers with stylish alternatives to usually ugly or at the very least boring tech acce